Title: Cancelled
Description: The planning process was cancelled and did not yeild a contracting process. For example, a buyer did not go ahead with planned consultations about the construction of a new recreational facility and decided not to build the facility.

Title: Unsuccessful
Description: The planning process is complete, but did not yield a contracting process. For example, a buyer completed consultations about the construction of a new recreational facility, but decided not to build the facility.
